      • computeSampleFleetStrengths

        public static void computeSampleFleetStrengths()
        Very approximately, the result is around 50 points of "effective strength" per point of difficulty. Lower (30-40) for pirates/Pathers, a bit >50 for some of the main factions. Not a lot of difference for standard/quality/quantity, since those adjust size etc to try to stay even.
